| 98 | 5.0 | 4.5 | 4.0 |
| 93 | 4.7 | 4.2 | 3.7 |
| 90 | 4.5 | 4.0 | 3.5 |
| 87 | 4.3 | 3.8 | 3.3 |
| 83 | 4.0 | 3.5 | 3.0 |
| 80 | 3.7 | 3.2 | 2.7 |
| 77 | 3.4 | 2.9 | 2.4 |
| 73 | 3.0 | 2.5 | 2.0 |
| 70 | 2.7 | 2.2 | 1.7 |
| 65 | 2.0 | 1.5 | 1.0 |
| 0 | 0.0 | 0.0 | 0.0 |

**Unweighted mode** uses the CP column for all courses regardless of level (max GPA = 4.0).

