## Course Row States

Understanding how a row is classified helps when entering data:

| Condition | State | Locked? | Optimizable? |
|-----------|-------|---------|--------------|
| Level = "Doesn't Count" | Excluded | Yes | No |
| Q1–Q4 + E1 + F1 all filled | Full year complete | Yes | No |
| Q1–Q3 + E1 filled, Q4/F1 missing | Planning row | No | **Yes** |
| Only "Course %" filled | Fixed final | Yes | No |
| No grades at all | Placeholder | Yes | No |

Only **planning rows** have their remainder adjusted by the spillover algorithm.

